videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond fires a quick pass to Ainias Smith for a 9-yard touchdown in the first quarter vs. Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Aggies' Smith spins into the end zone for TD) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Aggies' Smith spins into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Isaiah Spiller dives for the end zone and manages to keep his knees off the ground before crossing the plane for a second Texas A&M touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Spiller's impressive effort gives A&M another TD) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Spiller's impressive effort gives A&M another TD

videos.description: Texas A&M struggles with the handoff, fumbling the ball and allowing Arkansas' De'Jon Harris to scoop it up and score in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Spiller's fumble turns into Arkansas scoop-and-score) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Spiller's fumble turns into Arkansas scoop-and-score

videos.description: Ben Hicks sends a nice pass to Mike Woods in the end zone for a Razorbacks touchdown vs. Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hicks fires perfect pass to Woods for Arkansas TD) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Hicks fires perfect pass to Woods for Arkansas TD

videos.description: Kellen Mond finds Jhamon Ausbon who takes off for 12 yards but steps out at the 3-yard line. On the next play, Mond throws a TD to Quartney Davis for Texas A&M's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ausbon brings A&M to the 3, Davis hauls in TD) 2019/9/28

videos.headline: Ausbon brings A&M to the 3, Davis hauls in TD

videos.description: Arkansas QB Ben Hicks makes an impressive effort to bring the Razorbacks into Texas A&M territory in the final minute, but Cheyenne O'Grady couldn't convert as the ball slips through his hands.
